➜为啥同样是土味营销，巴黎世家被狂骂，老乡鸡却被捧出了圈？
http://www.sohu.com/a/418497146_425113	13983
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200915/b19f54fb994f43f7aeb68196fe8b60b6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200915/5687e53e90424c478969456491ace9e3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前段时间巴黎世家的七夕广告</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为土里土气被挂在热搜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让网友们嘲笑围观了一天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200915/9331ceaff5b244279763c78d1e1c116a.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
